===Noun===
'''blackberry''' (''plural'' '''[[blackberries]]''')
# A [[fruit]]-[[bear]]ing [[shrub]] of the [[genus]] ''Rubus''.
# The soft fruit borne by this shrub, formed of a black (when ripe) cluster of [[drupelet]]s.
# In some parts of England, the [[black currant]].

====Synonyms====
*(''shrub''): [[bramble]]

